Class Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cs309.loginscreen.Model.Task

  • public class Task
extends java.lang.Object
    Task Object for the All Task presenter. Upon receiving of the JSON package from ServerRequest, All Task parser parses the JSON array, and construct a Task object.
